{"type": "article", "id": 15499, "title": "这个插画师“环游世界” 80 天，靠谷歌地图和那本小说", "description": "一般人用地图来定位，而这位插画师却在地图里做了个环球旅行，并把他的旅途画成了明信片。", "date": "2015-09-24T17:45:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2059, "name": "插画"}, {"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 16592, "name": "环游世界80天"}], "category": 17, "author": 192992, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 235, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702165946ejKPFdalLMDSubwt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Lehel Kovacs </span><span>是一位来自布达佩斯的插画师，他从小就有一个梦想 </span><span>—— </span><span>像《环游世界 </span><span>80 </span><span>天》里的主人公 </span><span>Phileas Fogg </span><span>一样去周游世界。故事中，</span><span>Fogg </span><span>跟别人打赌，用 </span><span>2 </span><span>万英镑押注说自己将用 </span><span>80 </span><span>天</span><span>时间从伦敦出发去纽约，再一路穿过美国到达亚洲，最后返回伦敦完成一趟环球之旅。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span>Kovacs </span><span>也按照 </span><span>Fogg 的</span><span>路线去周游世界了，但却是在家里，确切地说，是在谷歌地图里。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"Kovacs 照谷歌街景图画的纽约布鲁姆街\" alt=\"Kovacs 照谷歌街景图画的纽约布鲁姆街\" src=\"img/uploads/20160702165943uCAoIpk5DsyB4EgS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Kovacs 照谷歌街景图画的纽约布鲁姆街</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>他用谷歌地图的街景功能造访了</span><span> Fogg </span><span>曾去过的 </span><span>40 </span><span>个地方，包括巴黎北站</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span>Paris </span><span>Gare du Nord</span><span>）</span><span>，纽约的布鲁姆街（</span><span>Broom\r\nStreet</span><span>），奥马哈的</span><span> </span><span>Durham </span><span>博物馆。然后他根据每个地点的街景图创作了一个</span><span> </span><span>“环游世界</span><span> 80 </span><span>天”</span><span> </span><span>的明信片系列。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"伦敦\" alt=\"伦敦\" src=\"img/uploads/20160702165943Y2ogdaN9RnG8HO7P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>伦敦</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"巴黎\" alt=\"巴黎\" src=\"img/uploads/20160702165944HtcBJekpaPZqs6QM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>巴黎</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"意大利布林迪西\" alt=\"意大利布林迪西\" src=\"img/uploads/20160702165945G0paTzsd47BvA36w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>意大利布林迪西</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"旧金山\" alt=\"旧金山\" src=\"img/uploads/20160702165945YwKq2SN47XIJFoBL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>旧金山</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Kovacs </span><span>先用铅笔手绘草图，然后将其扫描进电脑，再用</span><span> Photoshop </span><span>上色加工。在颜色的处理上，</span><a href=\"http://www.wired.com/2015/09/using-google-street-view-illustrate-around-world-80-days/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>他说</span></a><span>用了较为中世纪的复古色彩，以贴近故事里主人公生活的1873年。</span><span>“</span><a href=\"http://www.wired.com/2015/09/using-google-street-view-illustrate-around-world-80-days/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>看着这些明信片，有点以为自己真的去了这些地方。</span><span>”</span></a><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span>目前，他的</span><span> “</span><span>环游世界</span><span> 80 </span><span>天</span><span>” </span><span>明信片系列正在</span><span> Kickstarter </span><span>上进行众筹。截止至今，一共筹到了</span><span> 5400 </span><span>美元。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>图片来源： Wired</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}